com.planbase.pdf.layoutmanager.utils

Class Dim

  • com.planbase.pdf.layoutmanager.utils.Dim

  • public class Dim

    Immutable 2D dimension in terms of non-negative width and height. Do not confuse a dimension (measurement) with a Coord(inate) which represents an offset from (0, 0) at the bottom of the page. Remember: a Dimensions on a Portrait orientation may have the width and height reversed.

        public Dim swapWh()

        If true, returns this, if false, returns a new Dim with width and height values swapped. PDFs think the long dimension is always the height of the page, regardless of portrait vs. landscape, so we need to conditionally adjust what we call width and height.
